# Portal-specific headers.
#
# The portal is a daemon client. It must NOT be cached aggressively
# (a stale shell against a fresh daemon API is the worst kind of bug
# to diagnose), but should still hit the CF edge for SSL termination
# and global delivery.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()

/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache, must-revalidate

/
  Cache-Control: no-cache, must-revalidate
